Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything \Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.57,0:00:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.42,0:00:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I left everything this \Nworld has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everyone is in search of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jitto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:30.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:30.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:34.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:34.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:40.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:40.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,hata wo ageyou Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:45.56,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly the flag, Break of Romance Dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:45.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,namikaze tateyou suriipu kara no janpusutaato
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:50.85,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Make waves, jump from your sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:50.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,arienai sekai wo iku nara
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:55.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to go to the unbelievable world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:55.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kimi no tafunesu sore ga hitsuyou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:01:00.07,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,your toughness, that’s what it takes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:00.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,medachisugi sorette tsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:02.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Being brazen, is it a crime?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:02.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shimeitehai->tsumari Winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:05.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanted->means Winner:D
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:05.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,jiyuu dakega ore tachi no ruuru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:11.54,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom is our only rule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:11.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinpai nante dokofuku kaze--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:16.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not our way to worry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:16.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ttai one piece ichibannori
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.90,0:01:19.42,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,At any cost, One Piece, I’ll be the first
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume miru kokoro wa choo dekai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,My dreaming heart is huge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:23.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s important not to wake up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.53,0:01:27.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,samenai koto ga daiji--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:27.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.83,0:01:30.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:30.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Daybreak hasn’t come yet and I can’t wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yoake ga osokute jirettai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:34.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.75,0:01:39.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:39.86,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We...made it this far
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa...koko made kitaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:45.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We go...to where the dream is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ore tachi wa iku...yume no arika e
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:48.74,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t left anyone behind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:53.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dare mo oitekanaize--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:53.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going forward, that’s our pledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:56.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nshin aru nomi sore ga chikai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:56.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the day that the dream began
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:02:00.55,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yume ga hajimatta ano hi kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:00.55,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,the future that I’m \Naiming at hasn’t changed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:04.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,mezasu mirai wa onaji--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:04.63,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t stand still, I can’t stop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tto dekinai tomarenai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:07.30,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun of my heart will never set
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:11.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kokoro no taiyou shizumanai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:11.52,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:15.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:15.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:19.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:19.73,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, Sunshine four...WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:27.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ichi, ni, Sunshine yon...we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:35.36,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.92,0:02:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it \Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:03:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body \Nturned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.38,0:03:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and his crew reached the Fish-Man \NIsland located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where they instigated an all-out war \Nagainst the New Fish-Man Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy finally defeated \NHordy in a fierce fight
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thwarted his plot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.25,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.97,0:03:56.97,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Finally Time to Go! \NGoodbye, Fish-Man Island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.35,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FISH-MAN ISLAND--CORAL \NHILL "MERMAID CAFE"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Sharley,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin and his friends \Nare leaving the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Why don't you go and send them off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam! Can we go, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We'd need to close the cafe then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tourists will start coming back \Nsince that stupid Hordy is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I need you to give your best \Nfor the cafe like before, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on us, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The crystal ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't need it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.79,0:04:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never again try to see the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.15,0:04:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat destroying the Fish-Man Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:05:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted to see such a horrible future.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be so happy if my prevision \Nis not accurate this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is more afraid than anybody because \Nshe knows it was always accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future she saw may not happen soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.05,0:05:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be a year from now or more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.97,0:05:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason to \Nbelieve it wasn't accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Madam, Luffy-chin and his \Nfriends would never do such...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me for suspecting your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you want to say. I can \Ntrust the Straw Hat boy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are some gifts! Take them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.43,0:06:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama and everybody, are \Nyou really going to leave now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just became friends! Stay \Nhere at least one more day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! A week!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Just one more year!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.33,0:06:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been crying since the \Nfirst time we met, Yowahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will stop being a crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought the day like this would come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mermaid Princess of the Fish-Man Island
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who I've dreamed about is \Ncrying as we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna live here for a year or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.08,0:06:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sing about a dream life on the \NFish-Man Island on my latest single!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you wake up in the morning you \Nsay "Good mor-ningyo (mermaid)!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:07:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--In the cafe at the night, you say "Good eve-ningyo!"\N--Oh, my Mermaids!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stay here, Nosebleed-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just call me, Moss Head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling Moss Head, you fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Tamate Box that \Nthey gave to Big Mam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone opens it, there \Nwill be a huge explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.63,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doomed! One of the Four \NEmperors wants to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go to the New World just to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she'll forgive us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if we send all the treasures \Nthat we get from now on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot tell them that they \Nalready sent her a bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But those explosives are 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they won't explode, \NMinister of the Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, you are so positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the Ryugu Palace is very humid
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we don't even know if Big \NMam is going to open it herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's just hope for their safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two whispering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.61,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Log Pose for the New \NWorld. Take it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe you were going to \Ngo there with a single-needle one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new Log Pose? Wow, that's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are 3 needles. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the Log Pose that \Nyou have been using.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still moving a little bit! I thought \Nit gathered enough logs already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.32,0:09:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It did. And from now on, it would \Ntake only half a day to record logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the first half of the Grand Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you let the Log Pose record the \Nmagnetic waves of the next island
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and navigated your ship as it told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.25,0:09:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on the second half of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Grand Line, on top of the \Nsea current and the climate,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there are some islands that change their
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,magnetic waves, the only thing \Nyou can normally count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for some islands, the \Nmagnetic waves just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Then we can't reach those islands!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you only have one \Nneedle, you will get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.94,0:09:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if you have 3 needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them is moving just \Nlike the old one but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…the other two look settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They each record the magnetic \Nwaves from different islands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you can choose whichever \Nyour gut tells you and advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you live or die hangs on that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good navigator can tell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which way is safer to go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by looking at slight \Nmovements of the needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What it basically tells you is \Nthe wilder the needle moves,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more dangerous the island is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is happening on the island
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that is causing the change \Nin its magnetic waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I don't like this! I'd \Nrather not know about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see if it's dangerous?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Break that Log Pose!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You have to navigate \Nsafely in order to stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one in the middle is wobbling a \Nlot! That must be where the party is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-He was listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! You stay quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll choose which way to go from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I'm the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please Captain! Listen to what \Nthe navigator has to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san's so cute when she gets frightened!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So cute! So cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The B-side of the single \Nis "The Requiem for Us"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're ready to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.84,0:11:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Den-san taught me how to ascend too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.11,0:11:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.30,0:11:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna help with repairing the factory! \NAre you gonna be okay without a guide?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine! We had a lot \Nof fun on our way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's right! We don't need a guide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man's journey always ends up in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.65,0:12:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! We want a war, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.34,0:12:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody! Come visit someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the "All Blue" of my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheap dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want to say is "Thank you"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pray for your safe trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time we see you, we will lead \Nthe strongest army on the seafloor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh mambo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.42,0:12:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will become greater than the \NGreat Knight Neptune-mi-fa-so-la-ti-do!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Spread the sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.55,0:14:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.83,0:14:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Fish-Man Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to eat sweets and meat anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like humans now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.69,0:14:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Racoons and robots too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I give a damn, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh? What about bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Luffy-chin and everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.41,0:14:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to eat octopus balls again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys! I love you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We like bones too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.65,0:15:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yowahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can see you again someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I won't be a crybaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me out for a fun stroll again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A stroll? Do you wanna go to \Nyour mother's grave again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I want to go somewhere further next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.91,0:16:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to a real forest above ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you've never been \Nout of the sea, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you there next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.45,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! We have to help \Nyou keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san, a promise is something \Nyou have to keep at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Shirahoshi, I promise you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-chin-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all promise her so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...We won't let her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't cry anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not ever forget their kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy me a straw hat! I wanna \Npretend I'm the hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.39,0:18:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They only sell it above ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy one above ground then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are horrible humans \Nwho hate Fish-Men above...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.48,0:18:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I mean, I heard some \Nof them are like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there are good and \Nstrong humans like Straw Hat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Boss Jimbei! You came at the right time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will tell a merchant to get \Nhis hands on some of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what you want is that hero's hat, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a wonderful time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mermaid Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now everybody, pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.72,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no safe place once we sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:20:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to pass though the dark water again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.57,0:20:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that, Franky?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make the ship float with \Nbuoyant square logs of hollow Banyan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can adjust the speed by how many I put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.14,0:20:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ascend here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be at the sea where Shanks is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll leave this hat with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dear to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.38,0:20:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come bring it back to me someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:21:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you've become a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one thing that makes me wanna stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.51,0:21:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my desire to see \Nyou fulfill your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.34,0:21:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure that you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just think about the ones you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get back what you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you still have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Do you know what they call \Nthe second half of the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call the final sea beyond \Nthe Red Line by another name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.67,0:21:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:22:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sea where pirates who will open \Nthe way to the next generation gather.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.15,0:22:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate who conquers the sea will \Nbecome the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.23,0:22:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we pass through this deep sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll get to the ultimate sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.20,0:22:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally! I'll cut everything away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.20,0:22:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Laboon! One more half to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me! I'll navigate \Nyou anywhere you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.64,0:22:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The Sunny can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal you no matter how wounded you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never go hungry while I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.67,0:22:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got the warrior of the sea here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.77,0:22:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the New World!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.58,0:23:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats depart Fish-Man Island \Nand rise up out of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.24,0:23:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the harshest \Nocean of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the voyage up to the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.81,0:23:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they come across hardship after hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.64,0:23:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the crew is tossed about...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by a killer underwater whirlpool...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.62,0:23:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an unimaginable sight appears before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To the New World! Heading for the Ultimate Sea!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
